<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.6">
<l>taṇṭoṭu cakkarañ cārṅka mēntum taṭakkaiyaṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṭuyil koḷḷak karutik koṭṭāvi koḷkiṉṟā</l>
<l>ṉuṇṭa mulaippā laṟākaṇ ṭāyuṟaṅ kāviṭil</l>
<l>viṇṭaṉil maṉṉiya māma tīvirain tōṭivā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The eyes of him,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose broad hands hold the śārṅga bow and discus,</l>
<l rend="indent">along with a club,</l>
<l>wishing to sleep, he keeps yawning.</l>
<l>If [he] is not put to sleep, the breast milk that [he] drank</l>
<l rend="indent">will not be digested, you see.</l>
<l>Big Moon who remains in the sky, come running quickly!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
